      <title>高级官员称古巴准备接受外部投资</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/world/americas/cuba-us-foreign-investment-businesses.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统发表此番言论之际，古巴全国范围内停电，一名古巴高级官员表示，古巴将采取行动向外国投资者开放经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/world/americas/cuba-us-foreign-investment-businesses.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 09:41:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>海军上将的言论削弱了五角大楼的集束弹药政策</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/us/politics/cluster-munitions-iran.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第一届特朗普政府为集束弹药辩护为“合法”，但周一，布拉德·库珀海军上将谴责它们“本质上是不分皂白的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/us/politics/cluster-munitions-iran.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 09:03:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普官员考虑停止海上风电场的新计划</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/climate/offshore-wind-settlements-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《纽约时报》查阅的文件显示，拟议的和解方案将封锁纽约州和北卡罗来纳州附近的风电场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/climate/offshore-wind-settlements-trump.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 09:03:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉巴马州莫比尔的小妖精在 20 年后依然存活</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/us/mobile-alabama-leprechaun-st-patricks-day.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地一家新闻电视台报道了 2006 年 3 月发生的目击事件，在互联网上以及阿拉巴马州莫比尔市留下了深刻的印象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/us/mobile-alabama-leprechaun-st-patricks-day.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 09:02:30 GMT</pubDate>
