    <item>
      <title>陷入战争的海湾国家面临美国安全保障的限制</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/world/middleeast/iran-war-gulf-saudi-arabia-qatar-emirates.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于受到伊朗袭击以及对与美国安全关系价值的质疑，海湾国家已向乌克兰、澳大利亚和意大利寻求帮助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/world/middleeast/iran-war-gulf-saudi-arabia-qatar-emirates.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 09:01:46 GMT</pubDate>
