    <item>
      <title>根据特朗普命令，石油开始流经加州管道</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/santa-barbara-oil-pipeline-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2015 年管道破裂导致加州中央海岸发生环境灾难以来，石油一直没有流经该管道。这引发了特朗普政府和州官员之间的新斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/santa-barbara-oil-pipeline-trump.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 03:40:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普政府寻求在谈判期间罢免古巴总统</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/world/americas/trump-cuba-president-diaz-canel.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，美国已告诉古巴，为了让谈判取得有意义的进展，米格尔·迪亚斯-卡内尔总统必须下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/world/americas/trump-cuba-president-diaz-canel.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:54:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对伊朗的立场是什么？他们可以通过一句话来改变。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/politics/trump-iran-war.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统对提出相互矛盾的立场并不陌生，他的助手称这是他的谈判风格的一部分。但在伊朗问题上，他立场的转变与战争的后果发生了冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/politics/trump-iran-war.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>理查德·格雷内尔：从特朗普内阁希望者到前肯尼迪中心经理</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/politics/grenell-kennedy-center.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[理查德·格雷内尔曾希望成为特朗普总统的国务卿。相反，特朗普先生取代了他成为肯尼迪中心主席。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/politics/grenell-kennedy-center.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:04:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
